item.title: CVE-2020-6370|2024-08-04T09:02:40.564Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20netweaver%20%28di%20design%20time%20repository%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver Design Time Repository (DTR), versions - 7.11, 7.30, 7.31, 7.40, 7.50, does not sufficiently encode user-controlled inputs, resulting in Cross-Site Scripting (XSS) vulnerability.
